{#
  src/reporting/templates/gdpr_erasure_request.txt.j2
  GDPR Article 17 Right to Erasure (Right to be Forgotten) formal letter
  For EU and UK data brokers. References GDPR 2016/679 and UK GDPR.

  Required variables:
    company_name    (str)       — Full legal name of the data controller, e.g. "Pipl Ltd."
    user_name       (str)       — Full name of the data subject, e.g. "Jane M. Smith"
    user_email      (str)       — Email address of the data subject
    user_address    (str)       — Current postal address (single-line or multi-line)
    erasure_grounds (list[str]) — One or more grounds for erasure from the list:
                                    "no_longer_necessary"
                                    "consent_withdrawn"
                                    "article_21_objection"
                                    "unlawful_processing"
                                    "legal_obligation"
    date            (str)       — Letter date, e.g. "1 April 2026"

  Optional variables:
    user_dob        (str | None) — Date of birth for identification (YYYY-MM-DD or formatted)
    user_phone      (str | None) — Phone number for identification
    dpo_name        (str | None) — Name of Data Protection Officer if known
    region          (str)        — "EU" (default) or "UK" — selects applicable law references
    deadline_days   (int)        — Response deadline in days (default: 30 per GDPR Article 12)

  Ground codes map to Article 17(1) sub-paragraphs:
    no_longer_necessary  → Article 17(1)(a)
    consent_withdrawn    → Article 17(1)(b)
    article_21_objection → Article 17(1)(c)
    unlawful_processing  → Article 17(1)(d)
    legal_obligation     → Article 17(1)(e)

  Sample rendered output:
    [Your Name]
    [Your Address]
    [Your Email]
    [Date]

    To the Data Protection Officer / Privacy Team,
    [Company Name]

    SUBJECT: Right to Erasure Request — Article 17 GDPR
    ...
#}
{% if region is defined and region == 'UK' %}
{% set gdpr_ref = "UK GDPR (as retained in UK law by the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018)" %}
{% set authority_name = "the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO)" %}
{% set authority_url = "ico.org.uk/make-a-complaint" %}
{% set art12_ref = "Article 12 UK GDPR" %}
{% set art17_ref = "Article 17 UK GDPR" %}
{% set art21_ref = "Article 21 UK GDPR" %}
{% else %}
{% set gdpr_ref = "the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR 2016/679)" %}
{% set authority_name = "the relevant national Data Protection Authority" %}
{% set authority_url = "edpb.europa.eu/about-edpb/about-edpb/members_en" %}
{% set art12_ref = "Article 12 GDPR" %}
{% set art17_ref = "Article 17 GDPR" %}
{% set art21_ref = "Article 21 GDPR" %}
{% endif %}
{% set deadline = deadline_days | default(30) %}
{{ user_name }}
{{ user_address }}
{{ user_email }}
{% if user_phone is defined and user_phone %}
{{ user_phone }}
{% endif %}

{{ date }}

{% if dpo_name is defined and dpo_name %}
{{ dpo_name }}
Data Protection Officer
{% else %}
Data Protection Officer / Privacy Team
{% endif %}
{{ company_name }}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

SUBJECT: Formal Right to Erasure Request — {{ art17_ref }} (Right to be Forgotten)

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Dear Data Protection Officer,

I am writing to formally exercise my right to erasure under {{ art17_ref }} of
{{ gdpr_ref }}. I request that {{ company_name }} erase without undue delay
all personal data you hold about me as described below.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1. DATA SUBJECT IDENTIFICATION
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Full name:     {{ user_name }}
  Email address: {{ user_email }}
  Postal address: {{ user_address }}
{% if user_dob is defined and user_dob %}
  Date of birth: {{ user_dob }}
{% endif %}
{% if user_phone is defined and user_phone %}
  Phone number:  {{ user_phone }}
{% endif %}

Please search for my data under all of the above identifiers. If you
require any further information to locate my records in your systems,
please contact me at {{ user_email }} before the response deadline below.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2. GROUNDS FOR ERASURE
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

I request erasure on the following ground(s) under {{ art17_ref }}(1):

{% for ground in erasure_grounds %}
{% if ground == 'no_longer_necessary' %}
  [x] Article 17(1)(a) — The personal data are no longer necessary in
      relation to the purposes for which they were collected or otherwise
      processed. I did not provide consent for my data to be compiled
      and published by a data aggregation or people-search service.
{% elif ground == 'consent_withdrawn' %}
  [x] Article 17(1)(b) — I withdraw the consent on which processing is
      based, and there is no other legal ground for processing.
{% elif ground == 'article_21_objection' %}
  [x] Article 17(1)(c) — I object to the processing pursuant to
      {{ art21_ref }}, and there are no overriding legitimate grounds
      for the processing.
{% elif ground == 'unlawful_processing' %}
  [x] Article 17(1)(d) — The personal data have been unlawfully
      processed. Processing my personal data without a lawful basis
      under Article 6 GDPR constitutes unlawful processing.
{% elif ground == 'legal_obligation' %}
  [x] Article 17(1)(e) — The personal data must be erased for compliance
      with a legal obligation in Union or Member State law to which the
      controller is subject.
{% else %}
  [x] {{ ground }}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
3. SCOPE OF ERASURE REQUEST
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

I request that {{ company_name }} erases all personal data held about me,
including but not limited to:

  • Full name and any name variants
  • Current and historical postal addresses
  • Email addresses
  • Telephone numbers
  • Date of birth and age
  • Relatives, associates, or household members linked to my record
  • Employment information
  • Any photographs or images
  • Any inferred or derived data based on the above
  • Any unique identifiers (cookies, device IDs, advertising IDs)

I further request that {{ company_name }}:

  1. Ceases all further processing of my personal data;
  2. Does not re-collect or re-publish my data from public records or
     third-party sources after erasure;
  3. Notifies all third parties to whom my personal data has been
     disclosed ({{ art17_ref }}(2)); and
  4. Confirms in writing to {{ user_email }} that:
       (a) All personal data about me has been erased, and
       (b) All third parties have been notified of the erasure.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
4. RESPONSE DEADLINE
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Under {{ art12_ref }}, you are required to respond to this request without
undue delay, and no later than {{ deadline }} days from receipt of this letter.

If you intend to extend the response period by a further two months under
{{ art12_ref }}(3), you must notify me within {{ deadline }} days of receipt,
stating the reasons for the extension.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
5. RIGHT TO LODGE A COMPLAINT
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

If {{ company_name }} fails to comply with this request, or if I do not
receive a satisfactory response within {{ deadline }} days, I reserve the
right to lodge a complaint with {{ authority_name }}.

{% if region is defined and region == 'UK' %}
Information Commissioner's Office: {{ authority_url }}
{% else %}
Details of national supervisory authorities: {{ authority_url }}
{% endif %}

I also reserve the right to seek judicial remedy under Article 79 GDPR.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

I trust that {{ company_name }} will comply with its obligations under
{{ gdpr_ref }} and process this request promptly.

Yours faithfully,

{{ user_name }}

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
This letter was prepared by TraceBurn, a personal data removal tool,
on behalf of {{ user_name }}. TraceBurn is not a legal service and
this letter does not constitute legal advice. If you require legal
counsel, please consult a qualified data protection solicitor.
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
